title: Playable ART Cube
description:
The perfect game for the aspiring architect both young and old!
Manipulate twelve square and rectangle wood pieces, connected by elastic, to create a myriad of structures.  Enjoy limitless creativity.  

  • Ages:  6 years and up
  • Dimensions: 5.25 x 2.5 x 3.5 in.
  • Materials: Made from maple wood, each piece is colored in non toxic water-based dye.
  • Choke Hazard: No
